{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u25a0 <strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Here on a floating island high in the sky, Mana the summoner begins her adventure as she sets out to reclaim the &quot;Clay Pot of Darkness&quot; from an evil summoner!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u25a0 <strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is a top-down action game with high difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a stage-based 3D game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>1.Teleport anytime.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Even during an attack or when unable to act, you can consume MP to teleport nearby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>2.Can summon almost any enemy as an ally.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you defeat an enemy, they will drop an item (summon ball) that allows you to summon that enemy as an ally.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some enemies do not drop items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>3.You can get weapons used by enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you defeat an enemy, the weapon they are using will drop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some enemies do not drop certain items.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\u25a0 <strong>Game Controls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Supports keyboard, mouse, and gamepad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Gamepad recommended.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Story Progression 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3341330/41be6ada4405df6c55432f6057462e9671f8965a.jpg"},{"name":"Story Progression 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3341330/c2793c8e89d5f001ea33a079cf5ddc25376e